@1166 = ~Flail~
@1167 = ~Two Arguing Heads +2~
@1168 = ~This flail used to belong to a cleric of Tempus, who found it very difficult to make any decision, what was quite unusual for someone who needs to know how to act even during the greatest battles. Some say it was this weapon wasn't really helping and when he held it, he would overthink things even more.

