@1169 = ~War Hammer~
@1170 = ~Hammer of Powerful Yet Unlikely Blows +4~
@1171 = ~This hammer is an unusual weapons. While it can break any bone, damage metal plate armors, kill huge beasts like giants or dragons, it's very uncomfortable to hold and use. But if someone is able to land a proper hit, the effect may be truly grand!

