@1172 = ~Morning Star~
@1173 = ~The Pufferfish +3~
@1174 = ~This morningstar was blessed by a cleric of Umberlee. The name of this weapon was clearly inspired by its round head. Some say that this weapon and its name amuses even The Bitch Queen herself.

